==Personal life== In 2017, Hrefna got engaged to entrepreneur and actor [[Magnús Scheving]].<ref>{{cite news |author1=Stefán Árni Pálsson |title=Sjáðu þegar Magnús Scheving bað Hrefnu Bjarkar á ROK |url=http://www.visir.is/g/2017170109721 |accessdate=30 May 2018 |work=[[Vísir.is]] |date=3 January 2017 |language=Icelandic}}</ref>
